Action.author: jtonline
Action.body: Looks like this is due to the contract-metadata introduced in https://github.com/hyperledger/fabric-samples/commit/ec9eb7fa7308e7bac9182c7ca0bf0a77bcc16bf1

Action.author: davidkel
Action.body: Although the contract-metadata has been removed from the commercial paper example, it's likely that there is still a problem with the contract processing in 1.4.1 as surely a user shouldn't have to declare anything that is provided by the system contract.
